summary: A quite powerful dagger that can be found in Dawnstar Sanctuary (Dark Brotherhood quest line)
descriptionHtml: This is a quite powerful dagger that can be found in dawnstar sanctuary. It\'s the first thing I\'ve EVER done with the creation kit, so it\'s nothing advanced at all. If you download this mod, please comment if you think the dagger is too powerful or anything else. Locaton and how to install in the readme that comes with the mod
